WEBVTT

01:53.840 --> 01:54.840
Look at the time.

01:55.200 --> 01:57.080
Did they cancel the date?

01:57.960 --> 01:59.440
I'm sure he's at home.

01:59.840 --> 02:01.960
If they cancelled their date today,

02:02.400 --> 02:04.760
it means our job is done.

02:05.320 --> 02:07.520
Sisters united can overcome anything.

02:08.600 --> 02:10.360
Do you remember

02:10.560 --> 02:12.120
their expressions after you said that?

02:12.120 --> 02:14.040
It was like a bolt from the blue.

02:14.080 --> 02:16.160
They were dumbfounded on the spot.

02:17.079 --> 02:18.940
There is no disease we can't cure.

02:28.680 --> 02:29.960
Oh my god, no way.

02:30.360 --> 02:30.920
Let's go.

02:38.760 --> 02:40.360
I want to leave a good impression.

02:40.360 --> 02:40.960
It's okay.

02:41.240 --> 02:42.520
Just wait for me in the park.

02:42.520 --> 02:44.079
I'll be there after I change.

02:44.079 --> 02:45.040
Don't worry.

02:45.320 --> 02:47.180
I won't be late for our first date.

02:58.600 --> 02:59.600
What should we do?

03:01.520 --> 03:02.320
Calm down.

03:02.480 --> 03:04.740
Looks like all three of our plans failed.

03:05.600 --> 03:07.640
Grab the weapons and hit them hard.

03:24.760 --> 03:25.520
No.

03:25.840 --> 03:27.770
We can't let things go on like this.

03:31.000 --> 03:32.000
Grab the weapons.

03:34.720 --> 03:35.520
Let's fight.

03:45.000 --> 03:46.260
What are you two doing?

03:47.280 --> 03:49.440
We were about to ask what you two are doing.

03:49.440 --> 03:50.040
Yeah.

03:50.400 --> 03:51.460
What are you doing?

03:52.079 --> 03:54.000
Yuanbao, Qingyun.

03:57.680 --> 03:59.520
Gong Yu, what are you doing?

04:18.880 --> 04:20.320
I heard you're a good fighter.

04:20.320 --> 04:21.980
I heard you're not bad either.

04:22.200 --> 04:24.930
Mu Qingyun, I know you are the top guy in Zhicheng.

04:25.600 --> 04:27.040
But for me,

04:27.040 --> 04:28.400
I don't like being an underling.

04:28.400 --> 04:29.860
I only like being the boss.

04:29.920 --> 04:32.720
So give up your position.

04:36.240 --> 04:37.040
Sure.

04:37.200 --> 04:39.400
Take it if you can.

04:40.520 --> 04:43.120
Alright, let's see how well you can fight.

04:49.880 --> 04:50.240
Gong Yu!

04:50.240 --> 04:50.800
Qingyun!

04:51.120 --> 04:51.640
What are you doing?

04:51.640 --> 04:52.570
What's going on?

04:53.159 --> 04:53.690
Grandma!

04:54.360 --> 04:55.040
Grandpa!

05:02.440 --> 05:03.640
Are they classmates?

05:04.720 --> 05:05.560
Apologize.

05:06.160 --> 05:07.560
Come, shake hands.

05:20.080 --> 05:20.840
Wenying,

05:21.360 --> 05:22.360
it's you.

05:26.200 --> 05:27.280
It's you.

05:27.600 --> 05:28.280
Yeah,

05:28.920 --> 05:30.280
it's been so many years.

05:41.120 --> 05:43.040
To think that my grandpa and Yuanbao's grandma

05:43.040 --> 05:45.100
knew each other when they were young.

05:46.040 --> 05:46.640
Yeah.

05:47.200 --> 05:48.280
The thing is,

05:48.760 --> 05:49.840
it seems they're

05:49.880 --> 05:51.480
more than just acquaintances.

05:51.480 --> 05:52.940
You don't know my grandpa.

05:53.200 --> 05:54.440
After he went back that day,

05:54.440 --> 05:56.400
he combed his hair, looked in the mirror,

05:56.400 --> 05:57.640
and even dug out old photos.

05:57.640 --> 06:00.720
Do you think it's possible

06:01.000 --> 06:03.400
between my grandpa and Yuanbao's grandma?

06:05.160 --> 06:07.200
You sure have a wild imagination.

06:08.880 --> 06:10.410
I think it's highly likely.

06:10.720 --> 06:12.800
I think if we just give them a little push,

06:12.800 --> 06:13.800
and help them out.

06:14.440 --> 06:15.500
Is it appropriate?

06:16.120 --> 06:17.240
I don't know how your grandma

06:17.240 --> 06:18.720
has been doing all these years.

06:18.720 --> 06:20.180
But I think it's been tough

06:20.440 --> 06:21.640
for my grandpa alone.

06:21.640 --> 06:23.280
I hope after I go to college,

06:23.440 --> 06:25.520
he can find a companion to spend the rest of his life with.

06:25.520 --> 06:27.050
When you guys go to college,

06:27.120 --> 06:28.520
you wouldn't want Yuanbao's grandma

06:28.520 --> 06:30.250
to be home alone either, right?

06:30.360 --> 06:32.420
How about we talk to Yuanbao about it?

06:32.640 --> 06:34.760
Let's not tell Yuanbao for now.

06:35.560 --> 06:38.240
Because she still seems to have some prejudice against you.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.240
Besides,

06:39.800 --> 06:41.040
we don't even know

06:41.159 --> 06:43.240
our grandparents' true thoughts, do we?

06:43.240 --> 06:45.440
My grandpa is a rare, good man.

06:46.159 --> 06:48.159
You won't find another one like him.

06:48.840 --> 06:50.800
Our grandma raised Yuanbao and me.

06:51.080 --> 06:53.280
She is known as the queen of virtue.

06:53.640 --> 06:55.600
So many old men are lining up to woo her.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.000
She has high standards.

06:57.080 --> 06:58.159
She wouldn't settle for just anyone.

06:58.159 --> 07:00.200
My grandpa is quite a gentleman too.

07:00.760 --> 07:02.490
He wouldn't just like anybody.

07:02.520 --> 07:04.400
My grandma's cooking smells amazing,

07:04.400 --> 07:05.920
and she's great at everything inside and outside the house.

07:05.920 --> 07:07.600
My grandpa's skills aren't bad either.

07:07.600 --> 07:09.240
He dances square dancing so well

07:09.240 --> 07:11.480
that the old ladies in the team fight to be his partner.

07:11.480 --> 07:12.280
When my grandma was young,

07:12.280 --> 07:13.520
she almost became a singer.

07:13.520 --> 07:15.040
Even now, her voice is as good as Li Guyi's.

07:15.040 --> 07:16.520
Well, my grandpa...

07:16.520 --> 07:17.320
My grandma...

07:23.160 --> 07:24.020
How about this?

07:24.480 --> 07:25.610
I'll think about it.

07:26.280 --> 07:27.440
Okay, but hurry up.

07:28.640 --> 07:30.300
Since you are in Zhicheng now,

07:30.400 --> 07:31.860
I'll cover you from now on.

07:32.880 --> 07:34.409
Alright, I'll count on you.

07:36.440 --> 07:38.640
Where did you get this dirt from?

07:45.200 --> 07:46.640
So that's how it is.

07:47.760 --> 07:49.120
I'm sorry.

07:49.240 --> 07:51.000
I misunderstood you.

07:52.200 --> 07:54.260
I'm sorry. I apologize to both of you.

07:55.040 --> 07:55.840
Gong Yu.

07:56.640 --> 07:57.600
I'm sorry.

07:59.280 --> 08:00.960
What a mess.

08:03.800 --> 08:05.360
You guys were so secretive

08:05.440 --> 08:06.720
and kept me in the dark.

08:07.040 --> 08:09.360
Good thing the date didn't happen.

08:10.120 --> 08:10.760
Wait.

08:11.000 --> 08:11.640
Why shouldn't they

08:11.640 --> 08:13.000
give dating a try?

08:13.480 --> 08:14.960
You planned this for days

08:15.040 --> 08:16.170
without telling me.

08:16.360 --> 08:17.840
She's my actual grandma.

08:18.040 --> 08:19.240
What do you mean?

08:19.480 --> 08:21.240
What do you mean she's your actual grandma?

08:21.240 --> 08:21.840
Isn't she

08:21.920 --> 08:23.580
the same as my actual grandma?

08:23.760 --> 08:25.800
Besides, nothing's set in stone yet.

08:25.800 --> 08:27.200
If you knew earlier,

08:27.360 --> 08:28.600
it would've been ruined.

08:28.600 --> 08:30.280
It's not too late now.

08:30.400 --> 08:31.600
Good thing it's ruined.

08:31.600 --> 08:33.039
For something so important,

08:33.039 --> 08:35.000
how could you decide so easily?

08:35.600 --> 08:38.000
Besides, what kind of person he is,

08:38.080 --> 08:39.360
we still don't know.

08:42.400 --> 08:43.929
What are you talking about?

08:44.240 --> 08:44.800
Gong Yu.

08:45.120 --> 08:45.920
Sorry about that.

08:45.920 --> 08:46.960
She didn't mean it.

08:46.960 --> 08:48.480
She doesn't know you well yet.

08:48.480 --> 08:49.240
It's fine.

08:50.160 --> 08:52.800
It's just that Grandpa and Grandma were quite embarrassed just now.

08:52.800 --> 08:54.660
A perfectly good date was ruined.

09:01.080 --> 09:02.540
Since you know about this,

09:02.560 --> 09:04.040
you should think it over carefully.

09:04.040 --> 09:04.880
We'll see.

09:06.440 --> 09:09.240
Gong Yu, take Ruirui home later.

09:11.360 --> 09:12.880
What? Take Ruirui home?

09:13.160 --> 09:13.840
No.

09:14.320 --> 09:14.720
You two.

09:14.720 --> 09:15.250
Let's go.

09:15.520 --> 09:18.240
Grandma is waiting for us to go home for dinner. Hurry up.

09:18.240 --> 09:18.800
You two.

09:19.600 --> 09:20.400
Those two.

09:21.280 --> 09:22.640
Don't pull me.

09:29.840 --> 09:31.800
Let's go. I'll take you home.

09:54.840 --> 09:55.600
Mu Qingjun,

09:56.000 --> 09:58.120
you're really getting more and more opinionated.

09:58.120 --> 09:58.960
My friends,

09:59.240 --> 10:00.170
my grandmother,

10:00.400 --> 10:02.040
you can make decisions about them

10:02.040 --> 10:03.320
without my permission.

10:03.320 --> 10:04.600
Gong Yu is no good.

10:05.120 --> 10:06.850
His grandfather is even worse.

10:09.280 --> 10:10.120
Yuanbao.

10:12.240 --> 10:14.040
Yuanbao, listen to me, Yuanbao.

10:14.600 --> 10:16.360
Gong Yu is really a very good person.

10:16.360 --> 10:17.200
Trust me.

10:31.520 --> 10:32.560
Lately,

10:33.320 --> 10:36.160
I've been intentionally distancing myself from you.

10:36.160 --> 10:37.360
I apologize for that.

10:37.920 --> 10:41.120
Actually, I'm really not good at making friends,

10:41.560 --> 10:42.960
especially with girls.

10:43.560 --> 10:45.800
If I said anything that hurt you,

10:46.960 --> 10:47.800
I'm sorry.

10:52.480 --> 10:53.400
Why are you

10:54.120 --> 10:55.920
telling me all this so suddenly?

10:57.920 --> 11:00.720
Actually, I'm not very good at expressing myself,

11:01.000 --> 11:03.600
whether it's with friends or classmates.

11:05.040 --> 11:06.970
So I haven't made any good friends.

11:07.600 --> 11:08.880
As for Mu Qingjun,

11:08.960 --> 11:10.760
we became friends after a fight.

11:11.080 --> 11:13.410
And I happened to meet your grandparents.

11:15.880 --> 11:17.140
Do you have any dreams?

11:18.200 --> 11:20.840
My parents are both doctors.

11:21.320 --> 11:22.040
So,

11:22.960 --> 11:23.680
they hope

11:23.760 --> 11:25.420
I can be a doctor in the future.

11:25.840 --> 11:26.700
What about you?

11:28.560 --> 11:29.320
I

11:29.880 --> 11:31.960
want to be someone like Liu Xiang.

11:32.560 --> 11:33.880
To become an Olympic champion

11:33.880 --> 11:35.540
and win glory for the country.

11:36.640 --> 11:38.200
Your dream is so great.

11:39.360 --> 11:40.760
You can definitely do it.

11:43.000 --> 11:45.480
You see, we both have our own dreams.

11:47.880 --> 11:48.640
So,

11:50.800 --> 11:52.660
I really don't want to affect you.

11:54.680 --> 11:55.520
And,

11:56.320 --> 11:58.980
I'm really not good at being friends with girls.

12:11.000 --> 12:12.920
I understand what you mean.

12:13.840 --> 12:14.840
From now on,

12:17.080 --> 12:20.480
I won't force you to be friends with me anymore.

12:22.120 --> 12:25.200
Aren't we already friends?

12:25.560 --> 12:26.600
Nice to meet you.

12:34.040 --> 12:35.400
Nice to meet you too.

12:39.200 --> 12:39.880
Let's go.

12:47.280 --> 12:50.120
If Gong Yu's grandpa and my grandma get together,

12:51.560 --> 12:54.200
wouldn't Gong Yu become my older brother?

12:56.400 --> 12:57.760
If years later,

12:58.000 --> 13:00.000
Ruirui and Gong Yu get together,

13:00.440 --> 13:02.960
wouldn't Ruirui become my sister-in-law?

13:03.840 --> 13:04.600
Oh, my God!

13:05.200 --> 13:06.640
Gong Yu even hits girls.

13:08.840 --> 13:09.760
No, no, no.

13:09.840 --> 13:10.640
No, no.

13:10.840 --> 13:11.920
I absolutely won't allow it.

13:11.920 --> 13:13.520
I can't let them be together.

13:15.960 --> 13:17.020
What am I thinking?

13:18.000 --> 13:19.320
Study hard. Study hard.

13:19.320 --> 13:20.400
It didn't happen. It didn't happen.

13:20.400 --> 13:21.800
Study hard. Study hard.

13:45.800 --> 13:49.730
Leaving it at the door all night, aren't you afraid of attracting mice?

13:50.040 --> 13:53.000
Honestly, who apologizes like this?

13:54.640 --> 13:56.200
Don't think a piece of cake

13:56.360 --> 13:57.920
can buy me off.

14:37.920 --> 14:39.800
Every falling baby's breath

14:40.640 --> 14:41.840
is like the apple falling

14:41.840 --> 14:43.720
on Newton's head.

14:44.520 --> 14:45.720
Thump, thump.

14:46.280 --> 14:47.740
Landing right on my heart,

14:48.400 --> 14:49.960
making my heart flutter.

14:50.800 --> 14:52.720
So much so that ever since then,

14:53.080 --> 14:54.610
whenever I see this flower,

14:54.640 --> 14:56.640
I feel inexplicably excited.

14:57.120 --> 14:58.360
This silly blockhead

14:58.600 --> 15:00.920
always brings me joy and sorrow.

15:07.560 --> 15:08.520
Brother,

15:08.600 --> 15:09.080
Yuanbao,

15:09.080 --> 15:10.280
something happened.

15:11.640 --> 15:12.280
Look.

15:13.160 --> 15:16.200
Someone posted Yuanbao's photo on the forum.

15:46.680 --> 15:47.600
Who did this?

15:50.160 --> 15:51.560
It's you again, isn't it?

15:53.800 --> 15:55.040
What are you doing?

15:56.720 --> 15:57.680
It wasn't me.

15:58.720 --> 16:00.120
Don't falsely accuse me.

16:00.600 --> 16:01.520
Mu Qingyun.

16:18.240 --> 16:20.840
I believe everyone saw it on the forum.

16:22.680 --> 16:24.880
Yes, that was me.

16:33.480 --> 16:36.940
Thanks to the anonymous kind person for helping me promote it.

16:37.680 --> 16:40.520
From now on, if you have empty water bottles,

16:40.800 --> 16:42.060
you can give them to me.

16:43.680 --> 16:45.600
It really saves me a lot of effort.

16:46.200 --> 16:48.460
I don't have to look for them everywhere.

17:16.960 --> 17:18.089
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:20.240 --> 17:21.680
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:26.119 --> 17:26.800
Yuanbao.

17:27.920 --> 17:28.760
Keep it up.

17:30.040 --> 17:32.000
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:35.320 --> 17:36.560
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:36.720 --> 17:37.850
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:40.080 --> 17:41.400
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:44.280 --> 17:44.920
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:44.920 --> 17:46.050
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:47.120 --> 17:48.920
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

17:50.840 --> 17:51.520
Keep it up.

17:51.680 --> 17:53.520
Keep it up, Yuanbao.

18:04.800 --> 18:06.000
Thank you, everyone.

18:25.960 --> 18:27.680
Who is in charge of the sophomore forum?

18:27.680 --> 18:29.320
Yes, yes, it's me.

18:29.560 --> 18:32.120
Go delete the post about Xiong Yuanbao right now.

18:32.120 --> 18:32.920
Do you hear me?

18:33.520 --> 18:34.360
O-okay.

18:34.440 --> 18:35.960
N-no problem.

18:38.680 --> 18:39.400
Go.

18:39.760 --> 18:40.640
Let's go.

18:42.440 --> 18:45.040
Will they go to the dean?

18:46.400 --> 18:47.120
Really?

18:57.520 --> 18:58.280
Class,

18:58.720 --> 19:01.050
before we finish, I have an announcement.

19:01.440 --> 19:02.240
The triennial

19:02.240 --> 19:03.920
citywide middle school drama competition

19:03.920 --> 19:04.920
is starting soon.

19:05.120 --> 19:07.080
The rules require

19:07.400 --> 19:09.760
that the play cannot be negative

19:10.240 --> 19:11.280
or vulgar.

19:11.480 --> 19:13.680
The school will select one performance

19:13.760 --> 19:14.720
from the junior high and tenth grade

19:14.720 --> 19:16.400
to participate in the city competition.

19:16.400 --> 19:17.080
Of course,

19:17.560 --> 19:19.360
if you think it'll interfere with your studies,

19:19.360 --> 19:21.000
it's fine if you don't want to participate.

19:21.000 --> 19:21.800
No, no, no.

19:21.880 --> 19:22.920
Mr. Tian, we will participate.

19:22.920 --> 19:24.200
We're in. We're in.

19:24.440 --> 19:26.720
I knew you guys would want to join in.

19:27.000 --> 19:29.200
All right. Since you are in tenth grade

19:29.320 --> 19:30.960
and still have some free time,

19:30.960 --> 19:32.280
I'll give you this chance.

19:32.280 --> 19:35.000
Do you have any good suggestions for the theme?

19:36.120 --> 19:38.560
The judges this time are no longer limited to adults.

19:38.560 --> 19:39.640
The evaluation of peers

19:39.640 --> 19:41.080
also accounts for a large proportion.

19:41.080 --> 19:42.520
So our topic selection this time

19:42.520 --> 19:45.160
must also take into account the preferences of young people.

19:45.160 --> 19:46.800
I have also thought about this problem.

19:46.800 --> 19:48.560
Xing Yaqi, what do you think?

19:49.240 --> 19:50.080
Mr. Tian.

19:50.160 --> 19:52.680
I personally prefer foreign movies.

19:52.920 --> 19:55.120
And my favorite is "Gone with the Wind".

19:55.360 --> 19:57.640
I think the plot in it is very good,

19:57.680 --> 19:59.240
and the lines are also great.

19:59.240 --> 20:01.320
If we can take some classic clips

20:01.440 --> 20:02.920
and perform them,

20:03.000 --> 20:04.730
I think it should be quite good.

20:05.080 --> 20:06.520
Don't just say quite good.

20:06.520 --> 20:08.720
If we do it, we should do the best, right?

20:08.720 --> 20:09.440
Yes.

20:09.640 --> 20:10.520
Mr. Tian.

20:10.840 --> 20:13.320
I think domestic classics are also good.

20:13.400 --> 20:14.520
'Dream of the Red Chamber' is pretty good.

20:14.520 --> 20:16.440
If we add some music to it,

20:16.480 --> 20:19.240
we can perform Jia Baoyu and Lin Daiyu's

20:19.320 --> 20:20.640
poignant love story.

20:20.840 --> 20:21.520
Come on.

20:21.600 --> 20:22.800
Which girl in our class

20:22.800 --> 20:24.200
looks like Lin Daiyu?

20:24.520 --> 20:25.960
They look like Cheng Yaojin.

20:25.960 --> 20:27.160
Once they're on stage,

20:27.160 --> 20:30.000
"Brother Bao, where are you going?"

20:30.200 --> 20:31.530
Isn't that ridiculous?

20:33.960 --> 20:35.880
Don't you like 'A Chinese Odyssey'?

20:35.880 --> 20:37.080
Why didn't you say it?

20:37.080 --> 20:39.360
Everyone is talking about world classics.

20:39.360 --> 20:40.520
If I said 'A Chinese Odyssey',

20:40.520 --> 20:41.840
wouldn't I be laughed at?

20:41.840 --> 20:42.640
That's true.

20:47.640 --> 20:48.880
'A Chinese Odyssey'.

20:50.640 --> 20:52.600
'A Chinese Odyssey'?

20:53.120 --> 20:54.580
The one with Stephen Chow?

20:54.920 --> 20:56.120
'A Chinese Odyssey'.

20:56.280 --> 20:57.610
Why did you choose this?

20:57.680 --> 20:59.400
Because all the classmates like it.

20:59.400 --> 21:00.200
Do you like it?

21:01.360 --> 21:02.120
What about you?

21:02.120 --> 21:02.600
I like it.

21:02.600 --> 21:03.240
And you?

21:04.120 --> 21:05.920
See? The classmates all like it.

21:06.120 --> 21:06.880
Meng Jingu,

21:07.400 --> 21:08.600
you support this too?

21:08.880 --> 21:11.160
'A Chinese Odyssey' has elements of a Chinese classic,

21:11.160 --> 21:12.360
comedy and tragedy,

21:12.600 --> 21:14.600
and it fits the aesthetics of today's young people.

21:14.600 --> 21:16.000
This movie is

21:16.040 --> 21:17.320
quite popular among young people.

21:17.320 --> 21:18.380
Since it's a drama,

21:18.560 --> 21:20.680
no one says it has to be played like a classic.

21:20.680 --> 21:23.410
We can take a different approach and be original.

21:23.520 --> 21:25.440
Maybe we can win at one stroke.

21:25.800 --> 21:27.240
That sounds good.

21:27.840 --> 21:28.400
Sit down.

21:30.000 --> 21:31.520
So, what does everyone think?

21:31.520 --> 21:32.560
Sure, it's good.

21:32.600 --> 21:33.120
Agree.

21:33.200 --> 21:34.480
Let's perform this, sir.

21:34.480 --> 21:35.080
All right.

21:35.600 --> 21:36.480
Since you have decided,

21:36.480 --> 21:37.720
let's perform 'A Chinese Odyssey'.

21:37.720 --> 21:40.240
Although I think this is a bit risky,

21:40.560 --> 21:41.560
I'll say it again:

21:41.920 --> 21:43.720
As long as you work together

21:43.880 --> 21:45.120
and try your best in this competition,

21:45.120 --> 21:46.980
you are the champions in my heart.

21:47.000 --> 21:47.560
Okay.

21:51.720 --> 21:53.600
Since we are going to participate in the competition,

21:53.600 --> 21:54.120
should we

21:54.120 --> 21:55.720
choose a captain to plan it?

21:56.480 --> 21:57.360
Meng Jingu

21:57.480 --> 21:59.040
used to be a student council cadre

21:59.040 --> 22:00.440
when he was in Peiying Middle School,

22:00.440 --> 22:03.120
and he participated in the school anniversary of Peiying Middle School.

22:03.120 --> 22:03.960
So in this aspect,

22:03.960 --> 22:05.440
they might have more experience.

22:05.440 --> 22:06.370
So I propose that

22:06.520 --> 22:08.680
Meng Jingu and the class monitor, Xing Yaqi,

22:08.680 --> 22:09.840
be in charge of this planning.

22:09.840 --> 22:11.160
Does anyone have any objections?

22:11.160 --> 22:12.280
No.

22:12.640 --> 22:15.600
Okay, as for the participants,

22:15.840 --> 22:17.000
you can decide for yourselves.

22:17.000 --> 22:18.200
Voluntary sign-up is fine,

22:18.200 --> 22:20.120
and voting by everyone is also fine.

22:20.120 --> 22:21.680
But let me make it clear first.

22:21.680 --> 22:23.240
The midterm exams are coming up soon,

22:23.240 --> 22:24.320
so studies come first.

22:24.320 --> 22:27.440
Especially the bottom ten students in the monthly exam,

22:27.440 --> 22:28.600
if you don't do well this time,

22:28.600 --> 22:29.800
see how I'll deal with you.

22:29.800 --> 22:31.720
Got it.

22:32.880 --> 22:35.640
I'm looking forward to Yuanbao's version of Fairy Zixia.

22:35.640 --> 22:38.440
Also, whose turn is it for classroom duty?

22:38.560 --> 22:39.280
Teacher,

22:39.800 --> 22:40.560
our group.

22:40.720 --> 22:41.480
Gao Jingyi,

22:41.760 --> 22:42.880
regarding the toilets today,

22:42.880 --> 22:43.840
we still need two people to clean.

22:43.840 --> 22:44.900
Please arrange it.

22:45.560 --> 22:46.440
But, um,

22:46.520 --> 22:48.560
Wang Fei and Zhang Jiadong took sick leave today.

22:48.560 --> 22:49.560
They didn't come.

22:49.880 --> 22:51.880
It seems we don't have enough people.

22:51.880 --> 22:53.600
Are there any students

22:53.800 --> 22:55.480
who would volunteer to clean the toilets?

22:55.480 --> 22:56.810
Who would be so foolish?

22:57.840 --> 22:58.800
Teacher,

22:59.560 --> 23:00.480
I

23:01.120 --> 23:02.120
volunteer.

23:02.720 --> 23:04.280
There really is someone so foolish.

23:04.280 --> 23:06.800
Yuanbao, one person might not be enough.

23:07.320 --> 23:08.080
Teacher,

23:08.680 --> 23:09.800
leave it to me.

23:10.000 --> 23:11.240
I can do it alone.

23:11.640 --> 23:13.480
Okay, thanks for your hard work, Yuanbao.

23:13.480 --> 23:15.560
If you need more hands, remember to find a helper.

23:15.560 --> 23:16.440
Okay, sir.

23:16.960 --> 23:18.480
Alright, class dismissed.

23:18.480 --> 23:19.960
School is over!

23:20.040 --> 23:21.040
Let's go home.

24:03.320 --> 24:05.280
Our school used to be

24:05.400 --> 24:07.000
a prince's mansion.

24:08.160 --> 24:09.760
When the whole family was executed,

24:09.760 --> 24:12.160
many infants under a month old were killed.

24:12.960 --> 24:14.800
When night falls,

24:15.760 --> 24:17.420
they come out to seek revenge.

24:22.560 --> 24:23.760
Help!

24:24.280 --> 24:25.400
There's a ghost!

24:40.760 --> 24:41.560
What's wrong?

24:42.360 --> 24:44.640
There's a ghost inside!

24:58.760 --> 24:59.560
A ghost?

25:00.040 --> 25:02.370
I think you just have a guilty conscience.

25:02.600 --> 25:03.400
No.

25:03.520 --> 25:05.840
Listen, there really is a sound inside.

25:05.840 --> 25:07.240
It's so scary.

25:08.920 --> 25:09.720
Wait a minute.

25:10.160 --> 25:11.440
Wait, don't go in.

25:14.080 --> 25:15.340
There's nothing here.

25:22.960 --> 25:23.690
This side up.

25:28.040 --> 25:29.440
It's just a little kitty.

25:30.200 --> 25:32.600
Why is it crying like that? It's so scary.

25:32.880 --> 25:33.810
Special period.

25:34.320 --> 25:35.440
What special period?

25:35.440 --> 25:36.570
You don't know this?

25:36.800 --> 25:37.800
Animals

25:37.920 --> 25:39.240
go through something called heat.

25:39.240 --> 25:40.570
When they're in heat...

25:43.280 --> 25:44.080
Stop talking.

25:44.160 --> 25:45.400
I get it. I get it.

25:47.200 --> 25:48.800
Why are you two here?

25:48.960 --> 25:50.360
To see if you need help.

25:57.640 --> 25:58.880
The teacher asked me to come and check.

25:58.880 --> 26:00.480
The teacher didn't ask me to come.

26:00.480 --> 26:02.280
But we live opposite each other.

26:06.640 --> 26:08.640
Since you're done cleaning, I'll get going.

26:08.640 --> 26:09.640
Wait. Wait.

26:09.960 --> 26:11.320
Why don't we go together?

26:11.320 --> 26:12.720
It's all Shang Ningyu's fault.

26:12.720 --> 26:14.040
Telling ghost stories every day.

26:14.040 --> 26:15.100
Scared me to death.

26:17.080 --> 26:17.640
Mr. Liu.

26:18.040 --> 26:18.480
Hello,

26:18.520 --> 26:19.240
Mr. Liu.

26:19.600 --> 26:20.560
You scared me.

26:21.280 --> 26:22.560
Why haven't you left yet?

26:22.560 --> 26:25.160
Xiong Yuanbao just finished cleaning the restrooms on two floors.

26:25.160 --> 26:26.520
Okay, I'm leaving then.

26:28.920 --> 26:29.520
Wait.

26:31.120 --> 26:32.720
I'm here to use the restroom.

26:33.640 --> 26:35.700
You scared me so much I almost forgot.

26:36.080 --> 26:36.720
Well,

26:37.000 --> 26:38.800
Mr. Liu, should we wait for you?

26:38.920 --> 26:41.880
No need. You'll affect my performance if you stay here.

26:41.880 --> 26:43.480
Alright, we'll leave first.

26:46.800 --> 26:49.160
Won't Mr. Liu be scared alone?

26:50.200 --> 26:51.760
You think everyone is like you?

26:51.760 --> 26:53.620
There are no ghosts in this world.

26:53.640 --> 26:55.300
They're all made up by people.

26:57.280 --> 26:58.680
I know,

26:58.800 --> 27:00.280
but I'm still scared.

27:00.800 --> 27:02.240
If you're really scared,

27:02.680 --> 27:03.640
you can sing.

27:04.080 --> 27:05.960
The funnier the song, the better the effect.

27:05.960 --> 27:06.720
Give it a try.

27:07.200 --> 27:08.640
Really? I'll try it.

27:10.080 --> 27:12.000
The river flows east.

27:12.200 --> 27:14.530
The stars in the sky follow the Big Dipper.

27:17.440 --> 27:19.200
I think I feel a bit better.

27:20.080 --> 27:22.440
Give a roar when you see injustice.

27:22.480 --> 27:24.520
Strike when it's time to strike.

27:24.680 --> 27:26.040
Are you crazy?

27:32.920 --> 27:33.560
Desk mate,

27:33.840 --> 27:34.970
I'll be leaving now.

27:35.000 --> 27:36.880
Okay, bye.

27:37.200 --> 27:38.200
See you tomorrow.

27:38.800 --> 27:39.800
See you tomorrow.

27:39.960 --> 27:40.920
Bye.

27:42.960 --> 27:45.200
Why are you so nice to your desk mate?

27:46.280 --> 27:47.640
He's a new classmate,

27:47.680 --> 27:48.720
and my desk mate.

27:49.240 --> 27:50.360
He also helped me.

27:50.680 --> 27:52.760
What's wrong with being polite to him?

27:52.760 --> 27:54.200
What, are you jealous?

27:55.240 --> 27:56.600
Me, jealous?

27:56.880 --> 27:58.400
Are you thinking too highly of him,

27:58.400 --> 27:59.760
or too highly of yourself?

27:59.760 --> 28:01.280
Why would I be jealous?

28:02.440 --> 28:03.680
Why are you so mad?

28:05.160 --> 28:07.080
Didn't you already go back?

28:07.160 --> 28:08.420
Why are you here again?

28:08.640 --> 28:11.240
I just forgot something and came back to get it.

28:12.400 --> 28:14.320
Thanks for today.

28:15.400 --> 28:16.320
For what?

28:16.880 --> 28:19.320
Thanks for suggesting to everyone

28:19.360 --> 28:21.420
that we perform "A Chinese Odyssey".

28:22.600 --> 28:24.280
I just said it in passing.

28:24.400 --> 28:25.400
It wasn't for you.

28:26.080 --> 28:27.720
You're not nice to me at all.

28:28.440 --> 28:30.680
Why would I suggest performing "A Chinese Odyssey" for you?

28:30.680 --> 28:32.080
Don't flatter yourself.

28:33.960 --> 28:35.220
Who do you want to play?

28:36.600 --> 28:37.930
After thinking it over,

28:38.640 --> 28:40.680
Great Immortal Pansi suits me best.

28:41.760 --> 28:43.560
I'll just compromise

28:43.680 --> 28:45.410
and play Great Immortal Pansi.

28:45.760 --> 28:47.160
Compromise?

28:47.800 --> 28:49.660
Don't you just want to play Zixia?

28:49.920 --> 28:51.160
Yeah, so what?

28:51.400 --> 28:52.730
What do you want to play?

28:52.760 --> 28:54.880
Since you're playing Zixia,

28:55.600 --> 28:56.520
then I...

28:58.880 --> 28:59.520
Since we were kids,

28:59.520 --> 29:00.600
for this kind of performance,

29:00.600 --> 29:02.080
haven't you always been the boss?

29:02.080 --> 29:03.520
I'm hungry. Let's go eat.

29:04.280 --> 29:05.680
Why are you eating again?

29:05.800 --> 29:07.880
How about you play Zhu Bajie?

29:08.600 --> 29:10.320
You're the biggest eater here.

29:10.320 --> 29:11.800
You should play Zhu Bajie.

29:12.280 --> 29:13.680
How about you play the Bull Demon King?

29:13.680 --> 29:15.120
Then you play the Spider Demon.

29:15.120 --> 29:15.760
Bull Demon King!

29:15.760 --> 29:16.320
Spider Demon!

29:16.320 --> 29:16.960
You are the Bull Demon King!

29:16.960 --> 29:18.690
Spider Demon! Bull Demon King!

29:23.080 --> 29:24.560
You're so silly.

29:27.000 --> 29:28.530
Look at me, the Pansi Fairy.

29:30.440 --> 29:31.280
So silly.

29:39.200 --> 29:43.120
I'm not afraid to be alone.

29:43.520 --> 29:45.200
Courage as my blanket.

29:45.760 --> 29:48.120
Not afraid.

29:50.160 --> 29:53.520
No matter how dark the night is, I'll pretend not to see.

29:53.920 --> 29:57.360
The sun will definitely appear.

29:57.960 --> 29:59.440
Hello, look at me.

29:59.520 --> 30:01.320
What are you afraid of?

30:08.520 --> 30:11.520
Aren't you going on a business trip in a couple of days?

30:11.960 --> 30:13.520
Let's go see them first.

30:14.120 --> 30:16.440
Okay, let's go early tomorrow morning.

30:22.120 --> 30:23.450
It's been so many years.

30:25.520 --> 30:29.200
They should be the ones visiting us.

30:35.240 --> 30:36.440
All right, all right.

30:37.920 --> 30:39.080
Keep it a secret.

30:40.160 --> 30:41.640
We can never let the kids know.
